<style>
    .counter {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        width: 120px;
        border: 1px solid #0084ff;
        border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .counter button {
        background-color: #025a69;
        border: none;
        padding: 10px;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    .counter button:focus {
        outline: none;
    }
    .counter input {
        width: 40px;
        text-align: center;
        border: none;
        font-size: 16px;
    }
    .counter input:focus {
        outline: none;
    }
    .add-to-cart {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: left;
        }
        .add-to-cart button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #277e2a;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            top: 5px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .add-to-cart button:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }
</style>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="imgBx" style="background-image: url();"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h3>Jalape√±os Medianos<br><span>Diana</span></h3>
                <p>Ricos y crujientes frituras de maiz con un condimento 
                    picante para esos paladares enamorados del picante
                </p>
                <div class="counter">
                    <button onclick="decrement()">&#8722;</button>
                    <input type="text" id="number" value="0" readonly>
                    <button onclick="increment()">&#43;</button>
                </div>
                <div class="add-to-cart">
                    <button onclick="addToCart()">Agregar al carrito</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="imgBx" style="--img:url(/public/images/galletas.jpg)"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h3>Galletas Picnic<br><span>Diana</span></h3>
                <p>Dulces y crujientes galletas tipo wafer rellenas con un delicioso sabor vainilla de alta calidad.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>    
       
        <div class="card">
            <div class="imgBx" style="--img:url(/public/images/galletas.jpg)"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h3>Galletas Picnic<br><span>Diana</span></h3>
                <p>Dulces y crujientes galletas tipo wafer rellenas con un delicioso sabor vainilla de alta calidad.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>   

        <div class="carri">
            <img class="carrito" src="/stylesheets/image.png" alt="">
        </div>

        <script>
            function increment() {
                let numberInput = document.getElementById('number');
                numberInput.value = parseInt(numberInput.value) + 1;
            }
        
            function decrement() {
                let numberInput = document.getElementById('number');
                if (parseInt(numberInput.value) >= 1) {
                    numberInput.value = parseInt(numberInput.value) - 1;
                }
            }

            function addToCart() {
                let numberInput = document.getElementById('number').value;
                alert('Has agregado ' + numberInput + ' producto(s) al carrito.');
            }
        </script>
</body>
